  [Q] - Attack Light (10 stamina, 1.5s cooldown)
  [W] - Attack Heavy (25 stamina, 3s cooldown)
  [E] - Dodge (15 stamina, 2s cooldown)
  [R] - Defensa
  [F] - Defensa
  [Tab] - Cycle Target
  [F5] - Start Combat
  [F6] - End Combat
  [F7] - Print Debug Info"

